text: Rick Trickett is the current Assistant Head Coach and Offensive Line Coach for the Glenville State Pioneers and a former American football player.https://gscpioneers.com/staff-directory/rick-trickett/78 He served as the head football coach at his alma mater, Glenville State College in Glenville, West Virginia, in 1999. Trickett worked as an offensive line coach at a number of colleges, notably at Florida State University under Jimbo Fisher. ==References== Category:Year of birth missing (living people) Category:Living people Category:Auburn Tigers football coaches Category:Florida State Seminoles football coaches Category:Glenville State Pioneers football coaches Category:Glenville State Pioneers football players Category:LSU Tigers football coaches Category:Memphis Tigers football coaches Category:Mississippi State Bulldogs football coaches Category:New Mexico Lobos football coaches Category:Southern Illinois Salukis football coaches Category:Southern Miss Golden Eagles football coaches Category:West Virginia Mountaineers football coaches
